  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV2">
<l>āṟumāṟu māṟumāyo raintumaintu maintumāy</l>
<l>ēṟucīri raṇṭumūṉṟu mēḻumāṟu meṭṭumāy</l>
<l>vēṟuvēṟu ñāṉamāki meyyiṉōṭu poyyumāy</l>
<l>ūṟoṭō cai yāyavaintu māyavāya māyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Māyaṉ [born as] a cowherd,</l>
<l rend="indent">Having become the six [duties], the six [seasons], and the six [sacrifices];</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the unique five [great offerings], the five [oblations],</l>
<l rend="indent">and the five [fires];</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the highly excellent two [qualities], and the three [states],</l>
<l rend="indent">and the seven [qualities], and the six [qualities], and the eight [qualities];</l>
<l rend="indent">having become various [types of] knowledge;</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the truth along with the untruth,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the five [objects of sense]—including the sound—</l>
<l rend="indent">along with the sense of touch.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
